changelog from version 0.3 to 0.4 - released 2012.5.18

* New features
. full integration with HKPROF to profile every eZ Publish Page down to a single function call
. the csv file generated by the extension will have a 1st line with field names
. template operators have been added, allowing the developer to add perf. values to be logged from templates

* Bugfixes

* Changes
. the perf log files are stored default in var/log inside eZ and not anymore in /var/log
